<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Welcome to {{companyName}}!</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
        .header { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #52c41a 0%, #389e0d 100%); color: white; padding: 30px; text-align: center; border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0; }
        .content { background: #f9f9f9; padding: 40px; border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px; }
        .button { display: inline-block; background: #52c41a; color: white; padding: 15px 30px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; margin: 10px; font-weight: bold; }
        .footer { text-align: center; margin-top: 30px; color: #666; font-size: 14px; }
        .feature-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 20px; margin: 20px 0; }
        .feature-item { background: white; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; text-align: center; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h1>🎉 Welcome to {{companyName}}!</h1>
        <p>Your {{userType}} account is now active and ready to use</p>
    </div>

    <div class="content">
        <p>Hi {{userName}},</p>

        <p>Congratulations! Your email has been verified and your {{companyName}} {{userType}} account is now fully activated. You're now part of our growing community of influencers and businesses!</p>

        <div style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
            <a href="{{dashboardUrl}}" class="button">Go to Dashboard</a>
            <a href="{{loginUrl}}" class="button" style="background: #1890ff;">Sign In</a>
        </div>

        <h3>🚀 What's Next?</h3>

        {{#if (eq userType "creator")}}
        <div class="feature-grid">
            <div class="feature-item">
                <h4>📱 Connect Social Accounts</h4>
                <p>Link your Instagram, TikTok, and YouTube accounts to start showcasing your content.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-item">
                <h4>🎯 Browse Campaigns</h4>
                <p>Discover exciting brand campaigns that match your niche and audience.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-item">
                <h4>💎 Create Content</h4>
                <p>Submit your best work and get it approved by brands for payment.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-item">
                <h4>💰 Get Paid</h4>
                <p>Earn money for your approved content and grow your influence.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        {{else}}
        <div class="feature-grid">
            <div class="feature-item">
                <h4>🎯 Create Campaigns</h4>
                <p>Launch marketing campaigns to reach your target audience through creators.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-item">
                <h4>👥 Find Creators</h4>
                <p>Discover talented content creators who align with your brand values.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-item">
                <h4>📊 Track Performance</h4>
                <p>Monitor campaign analytics and measure your marketing ROI.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-item">
                <h4>💳 Manage Payments</h4>
                <p>Handle transactions securely with our integrated payment system.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        {{/if}}

        <h3>📚 Getting Started Resources</h3>
        <ul>
            <li>📖 <a href="#" style="color: #1890ff;">Platform Guide</a> - Learn how to use {{companyName}} effectively</li>
            <li>💡 <a href="#" style="color: #1890ff;">Best Practices</a> - Tips for success on our platform</li>
            <li>🎥 <a href="#" style="color: #1890ff;">Video Tutorials</a> - Step-by-step walkthroughs</li>
            <li>❓ <a href="#" style="color: #1890ff;">FAQ</a> - Answers to common questions</li>
        </ul>

        <p>We're excited to have you on board and can't wait to see what you'll achieve with {{companyName}}!</p>

        <p>Happy creating (or campaigning)!</p>
        <p><strong>The {{companyName}} Team</strong></p>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
        <p>Need help getting started? Contact us at <a href="mailto:{{supportEmail}}">{{supportEmail}}</a></p>
        <p>&copy; 2024 {{companyName}}. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>